Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.34,0:00:16.74,Title,,0,0,0,,Sweet Mari
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.90,0:12:36.98,end,,0,0,0,,End
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,------------------------------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.04,0:00:19.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Sweet in the mouth,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.08,0:00:20.12,Default,,0,0,0,,sweet in the heart;
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.00,0:00:22.60,Default,,0,0,0,,With the Meigan Birthday Cake,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.56,0:00:26.04,Default,,0,0,0,,let love and friendship melt together
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.04,0:00:28.76,Default,,0,0,0,,on this most special day of the year!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.80,0:00:31.08,Default,,0,0,0,,What a pretty cake!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.44,0:00:34.20,Default,,0,0,0,,My birthday is in a few days.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.64,0:00:36.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.28,0:00:37.88,Default,,0,0,0,,why don’t we have a birthday party?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.96,0:00:50.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Who should I invite to my birthday party?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.08,0:00:56.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomorrow is my birthday—
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.12,0:01:05.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Your garbage fell out;
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.48,0:01:06.44,Default,,0,0,0,,be more aware next time!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.04,0:01:14.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Where’d they go?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.44,0:01:22.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I’d like to invite you to my—
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.12,0:01:29.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You’re in violation of overloading;
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.80,0:01:31.32,Default,,0,0,0,,overloaded passengers, get off immediately!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.96,0:01:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Be more aware next time!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.52,0:01:44.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do people run the moment they see me?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.20,0:01:47.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Slow down!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.00,0:01:47.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You’re speeding!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.52,0:01:53.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Apparently, I look so mean!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.68,0:01:56.84,Default,,0,0,0,,No wonder everyone is afraid of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.28,0:02:01.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop yelling!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.40,0:02:02.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Hand over the fragment!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.56,0:02:04.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay away!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.84,0:02:08.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I won’t give you the fragment!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.56,0:02:15.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You can run all you want,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.48,0:02:17.64,Default,,0,0,0,,but I’ll get it no matter what!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.08,0:02:21.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.60,0:02:23.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.68,0:02:26.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Don’t bully Tibbie!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.68,0:02:31.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Tibbie’s such a sweet girl;
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.08,0:02:32.84,Default,,0,0,0,,how could you possibly treat her like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.84,0:02:38.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Sirius!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.52,0:02:47.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.56,0:02:51.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Still not giving up, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.76,0:02:53.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Ma—Mari?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.20,0:03:04.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Tibbie,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.92,0:03:05.56,Default,,0,0,0,,are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.56,0:03:06.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.44,0:03:09.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I’m okay;
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.32,0:03:10.68,Default,,0,0,0,,thank you, Sister Mari!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.08,0:03:14.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Tibbie…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.80,0:03:18.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Could you teach me to be a little sweeter?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.36,0:03:21.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.96,0:03:23.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I usually act so serious,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.84,0:03:25.96,Default,,0,0,0,,and everyone is afraid of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.00,0:03:28.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to become sweeter
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.68,0:03:30.92,Default,,0,0,0,,so that people will want to come to my birthday party.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.72,0:03:32.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Birthday party?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.28,0:03:41.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I can give it a try!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.92,0:03:43.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.36,0:03:46.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Then let’s get started!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.68,0:03:58.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You think I can’t go fragment searching myself
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.04,0:03:59.48,Default,,0,0,0,,if I can’t snatch it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.44,0:04:06.12,Default,,0,0,0,,The fragment is right up ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.52,0:04:11.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Out of my way!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.44,0:04:18.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I… I’m just passing by!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.12,0:04:48.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Is Mari planning a birthday party?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.76,0:05:07.08,Default,,0,0,0,,What a coincidence; we’ve crossed paths again!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.04,0:05:17.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Apologies for the wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.36,0:05:23.64,Default,,0,0,0,,How beautiful!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.32,0:05:40.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.60,0:05:46.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Don’t you know that you were speeding just now?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.60,0:05:51.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like relying on appearances isn’t enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.08,0:05:54.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.88,0:05:57.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Mari, I think
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.24,0:05:59.24,Default,,0,0,0,,you should change your serious facial expressions
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.76,0:06:02.92,Default,,0,0,0,,and smile a little bit more.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.36,0:06:05.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Like… Like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.32,0:06:08.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Smile naturally!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.16,0:06:10.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Just like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.72,0:06:12.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.36,0:06:15.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Just like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.68,0:06:26.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Don’t forget to smile!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.16,0:06:32.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You were speeding just now;
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.76,0:06:34.44,Default,,0,0,0,,be more aware next time!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.48,0:06:54.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.36,0:06:55.24,Default,,0,0,0,,This is bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.24,0:06:57.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Mari is definitely going to punish them!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.76,0:07:03.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.76,0:07:05.96,Default,,0,0,0,,okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.92,0:07:10.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Don’t skate on the road next time;
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.16,0:07:12.20,Default,,0,0,0,,that’s very dangerous!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.56,0:07:14.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that actually Mari?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.80,0:07:17.16,Default,,0,0,0,,She seems different!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.28,0:07:21.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I’m planning a birthday party;
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.08,0:07:23.08,Default,,0,0,0,,would you like to attend?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.44,0:07:26.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure, I’d love to!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.56,0:07:30.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Would everyone like to come to my birthday party?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.24,0:07:33.16,Default,,0,0,0,,There’s going to be delicious cake!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.68,0:07:35.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to come!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.58,0:07:36.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Me too!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.24,0:07:40.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to come!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.92,0:07:42.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I’m going to get an invitation, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.96,0:07:45.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to come to your birthday party, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.80,0:07:59.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I’m going to get an invitation!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.44,0:08:01.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to come!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.44,0:08:06.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Remember to show up!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.52,0:08:07.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to come, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.20,0:08:15.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Without an invitation,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.48,0:08:17.00,Default,,0,0,0,,how am I supposed to get in?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.00,0:08:19.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Tibbie,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.80,0:08:20.84,Default,,0,0,0,,thanks to you,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.84,0:08:23.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I was able to invite so many friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.56,0:08:24.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You’re welcome!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.28,0:08:28.20,Default,,0,0,0,,We’re almost all set.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.88,0:08:31.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are the sardines?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.68,0:08:34.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I saw that they were tired after working for so long,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.16,0:08:36.76,Default,,0,0,0,,so I let them rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.88,0:08:39.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.32,0:08:40.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Then let’s get ready
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.68,0:08:42.28,Default,,0,0,0,,to welcome the guests!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.24,0:08:43.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.56,0:08:47.56,Default,,0,0,0,,The sardines are gone,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.56,0:08:50.52,Default,,0,0,0,,and the now-sweet Mari isn’t scary anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.24,0:08:58.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Happy birthday,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.52,0:08:59.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Mari!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.24,0:09:02.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.92,0:09:06.68,Default,,0,0,0,,This gift is for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.20,0:09:09.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.64,0:09:16.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Wolffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.04,0:09:21.16,Default,,0,0,0,,How could you have a birthday party without me, Wolffy?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.24,0:09:26.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Out of my way!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.20,0:09:28.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Don’t try to stop King Wolffy from his fragment search!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.60,0:09:43.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.76,0:09:46.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I ask you to please leave my birthday party!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.80,0:09:50.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I’ll leave once I find the fragment!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.16,0:09:57.24,Default,,0,0,0,,The fragment might just be in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.48,0:10:02.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.20,0:10:04.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Wolffy,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.08,0:10:07.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I won’t let you ruin Sister Mari’s birthday party!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.88,0:10:12.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you really think you, a single little goat, can stop me?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.88,0:10:17.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Don’t underestimate me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.52,0:10:25.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Don’t panic, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.68,0:10:31.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Tibbie!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.36,0:10:35.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Wolffy,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.36,0:10:38.12,Default,,0,0,0,,please let go of Tibbie,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.44,0:10:39.00,Default,,0,0,0,,would you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.00,0:10:43.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I’m not afraid of you anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.04,0:10:52.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Tibbie!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.04,0:10:55.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Don’t hurt my friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.88,0:11:14.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I’ll be back!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.00,0:11:23.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.32,0:11:26.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I’m okay,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.76,0:11:27.48,Default,,0,0,0,,but
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.52,0:11:30.52,Default,,0,0,0,,all of the guests got scared off.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.48,0:11:35.72,Default,,0,0,0,,There’s no one to celebrate my birthday with again.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.24,0:11:38.28,Default,,0,0,0,,There’s me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.84,0:11:40.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Tibbie!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.92,0:11:42.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Us, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.24,0:11:47.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn’t I scare you guys off?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.36,0:11:50.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You keep the seas in order;
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.28,0:11:51.80,Default,,0,0,0,,how could we possibly be afraid of you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.08,0:11:55.48,Default,,0,0,0,,We just went and hid the cake!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.56,0:11:58.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.16,0:12:00.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Let’s have some cake!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.08,0:12:02.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.36,0:12:10.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.84,0:12:19.64,Default,,0,0,0,,It’s a fragment!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.96,0:12:22.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Mari,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.84,0:12:24.52,Default,,0,0,0,,can I have this fragment?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.32,0:12:27.48,Default,,0,0,0,,If you like it, you can have it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.28,0:12:29.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Mari!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.60,0:12:31.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You’re welcome!
